  chapter: 7
  number: 30
  title: Space Station
  description: "Use gravity switches to navigate through the space station\u2019s
    inverted corridors. The player flips gravity to move across ceilings, walls,
    and platforms while avoiding enemies. Find the key and reach the cockpit room
    to escape the station."
  objectives: "Flip gravity to move through the station\u2019s upper and lower pathways.\n\nAvoid
    obstacles and alien patrols while navigating each section.\n\nLocate the key
    hidden somewhere inside the station.\n\nReach the cockpit door and unlock it
    using the key."
