  - icon: 3
    name: Freeplay > Minigame 7
    description: Space Station
  instructions: '1.Press the left and right arrows to move horizontally.


    2.Step
    on or activate GRAVITY switches to flip gravity up or down.


    3.Use timing
    to avoid enemies while upside down or right-side up.


    4. Collect the key
    to unlock the cockpit room.


    5. Reach the green flag or cockpit entrance
    to complete the mission.'
